		"description": "Complete API documentation for the Point of Sale (POS) system. This collection includes all endpoints for authentication, products, customers, sales, and file uploads.\n\n## Base URL\n- Production: `https://your-production-url.com`\n- Local: `http://localhost:3000`\n\n## Authentication\nMost endpoints require JWT authentication. After logging in or registering, use the `accessToken` from the response in the Authorization header as a Bearer token.\n\n## Variables\nSet these variables in your Postman environment:\n- `baseUrl`: Your API base URL\n- `accessToken`: JWT access token (auto-set after login)\n- `refreshToken`: JWT refresh token (auto-set after login)",
